# FishStomachs

<!-- badges: start -->
<!-- badges: end -->

FishStomachs is a package for compilation of stomach contents into population diet and food rations.

## Installation

You can install the development version from [GitHub](https://github.com/) with:

``` r
# install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("MortenVinther/FishStomachs")

# or to get the full documentation
devtools::install_github("MortenVinther/FishStomachs",build_manual=TRUE,build_vignettes=TRUE)
```
## Examples

The Vignettes, Example 1 - Example 5 show you how to use **FishStomachs**.
